Comment: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ignore it.
Comment: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand that, right?
Comment: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so! If the PTO would move in solidarity with the school
Comment: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we can prevent problems like that,
Comment: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we had informal consent to that effect!
Comment: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I do think the PTO was also rather hasty on that front.
Comment: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that informal consent was simply in regards\Nto how the prom looked on paper, no?
Comment: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't make sense!
Comment: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We talk to them in advance\Nso that things don't get overturned later on!
Comment: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyways, isn't it the parent's job to discipline their kids
Comment: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so problems like that don't hap-
Comment: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's wise to forge ahead with prom\Nwhile there are vocal detractors.
Comment: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The thank-you party is for the graduating students,
Comment: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but its also an important event for the PTO,
Comment: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the teachers, and other members of the community.
Comment: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody has expressed discontent with the thank-you parties thrown in previous years, correct?
Comment: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the thank-you parties thrown in previous years, correct?
Comment: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're considering graduating students,
Comment: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we're also going to be graduating students in the future.
Comment: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the right to propose things\Nregarding the thank-you party.
Comment: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we've gotten\Na mostly positive response from social me-
Comment: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be the case on social media.
Comment: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's also crucial to listen to the opinions\Nthat are not out in the open.
Comment: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The're pretty much in a deadlock.
Comment: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I now totally understand what Haruno Yukinoshita meant
Comment: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when she said her mom was scarier than she is.
Comment: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She puts on a soft smile
Comment: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and appears to consider the other side's opinion,
Comment: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's all a front for her counter style\Nthat lures them unwittingly
Comment: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something you all need to keep in mind.
Comment: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,into a trap that was set from the very beginning.
Comment: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This is someone you can't fight using logic.
Comment: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The school gave informal consent, right?\NWhat is their stance on all this?
Comment: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally speaking, I'm against the idea\Nof immediately cancelling the prom.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At this school we have a history\Nof placing value on the autonomy of our students.
Comment: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We should make the appropriate modifications\Nand ask for the support of the PTO members,
Comment: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and continue to have\Nintermittent discussions about this...
Comment: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is my opinion on the matter.
Comment: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with your opinion.
Comment: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I will return again for further discussions.
Comment: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino.
Comment: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're working very hard.\NBut please, come home earlier, okay?
Comment: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to push yourself.
Comment: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Comment: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was rough.
Comment: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose\Nthe school's response to this will be?
Comment: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say.
Comment: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, as it pertains to the video\Ngetting uploaded to social media,
Comment: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I... well, my superiors and I don't see it as a problem.
Comment: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are a lot of gracious people out there who love sharing their thoughts with the higher-ups.
Comment: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who love sharing their thoughts with the higher-ups.
Comment: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If they come this far to make their voices heard,\Nthen we have to respond appropriately.
Comment: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose the school can't appeal to the PTO, can they?
Comment: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ways of getting that done, sure...
Comment: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to do more proms in the future,
Comment: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then I think it's best that I not get involved.
Comment: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuka, you haven't told them yet?
Comment: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't talk about things\Nthat haven't been made official yet.
Comment: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't say it, can you?
Comment: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... no...
Comment: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, they should already have figured it out
Comment: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,based on how many years you've been at this school.
Comment: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you mean...
Comment: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can talk about that later.
Comment: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what will you do?
Comment: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tweak all the imperfections in the plan...
Comment: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll just have to think of a way to convince them\Nduring the future meetings.
Comment: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds right. First, we'll gather materials\Nto persuade them, and then...
Comment: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Comment: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The student council will handle everything from here.
Comment: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something I must do.
Comment: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be splitting hairs.
Comment: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Being the big brother again?
Comment: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?
Comment: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just help Yukino out all the time.
Comment: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't her big brother or anything like that.
Comment: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it.
Comment: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's important to us, so of course\Nwe'll lend her a hand and help her out.
Comment: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that if you truly value someone,\Nthen you should respect their wishes.
Comment: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If the prom happens, then mom's impression\Nof Yukino may change to some extent.
Comment: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's only if Yukino\Ndoes it on her own without help.
Comment: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you understand\Nwhat getting involved would mean?
Comment: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're convinced it's for their benefit,
Comment: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,lending someone a hand isn't always the right choice.
Comment: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the term\Nis for relationships like yours?
Comment: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruno, stop.
Comment: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They get it.
Comment: 0,0:14:56.17,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to prove that I can do it on my own.
Comment: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So Hikigaya...
Comment: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask for your help anymore.
Comment: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, then I'll gradually become useless.
Comment: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pushed so much onto both you
Comment: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and Yuigahama, all while claiming I wouldn't rely on anyone.
Comment: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't true. You're completely wrong...
Comment: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true.
Comment: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The end result is always the same.
Comment: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I thought I could do better, the truth is nothing has changed.
Comment: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please...
Comment: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know the answer?
Comment: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,About Yukino, and 'Gahama, and you...\Nthe relationship between you three...
Comment: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A-a love triangle or something...
Comment: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that seriously what you think?
Comment: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but laugh at the fact that you said it yourself!
Comment: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, m-my stomach! That was hilarious! Ah, it hurts!
Comment: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not THAT funny...
Comment: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the right answer?
Comment: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The right answer?  Oh, the right answer!
Comment: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The right answer is...
Comment: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called codependency.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before, didn't I? It isn't trust.
Comment: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels nice having her rely on you though, right?
Comment: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But that codependency you had is over now.
Comment: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino will now learn to be independent\Nand become an adult.
Comment: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is she giving up on\Nto become an adult, then?
Comment: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as me, a whole lot of something.
Comment: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, class, take your seats.
Comment: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikky.
Comment: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Comment: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we talked about making a cake from scratch, right?
Comment: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I told my mom and she said we could do it at my house.
Comment: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know, my mom is actually excited\Nabout it and it's pretty embarrassing!
Comment: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hesitant to go... I'm even more hesitant\Nafter hearing that second part.
Comment: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we're at your house, Komachi will find out what we're doing.
Comment: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's somewhere we can go...
Comment: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Comment: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's trouble with the prom.
Comment: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Comment: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this I hear about the school\Ndeciding to cancel the prom?
Comment: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain another day.\NI'm still busy dealing with it right now.
Comment: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days is it gonna take for that?
Comment: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll lose any chance of making this work if we have to wait for details.
Comment: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you want to help with the prom?
Comment: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah... I mean...
Comment: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to tell you then, don't I?
Comment: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The news about prom being cancelled\Nwasn't told to you under Yukinoshita's wishes.
Comment: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you understand what that means.\NI'll ask you straight.
Comment: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that, do you still have a reason\Nto help with the prom?
Comment: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I won't understand if you clam up on a phone call.\NThat's a bad habit of yours.
Comment: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it into words. I'll wait.
Comment: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs70}Thành ngữ, đại ý là không thể dừng trên đường một khi đã lên thuyền.
Comment: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,乗りかかった船,Lý do là... giống như với clb, em đã đi quá xa để dừng lại.
Comment: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly put this into words...\NIt's something important, so I can't say it.
Comment: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think things over, take careful action,\Nand avoid mistakes to assure I'm understood...
Comment: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the same thing, right?
Comment: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how you didn't say anything\Nabout leaving the school!
Comment: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya, I'm sorry. Still, I'll keep waiting.
Comment: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So put it into words.
Comment: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I promised her I would save her someday.
Comment: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it. I'll make time.
Comment: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get here now.
Comment: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry you had to wait.\NI'm going to go see Miss Hiratsuka for a bit.
Comment: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. What are you going there for?
Comment: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To get a better grasp of the situation, for starters.
Comment: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... but with you there,\Nthen I think things will work out in the end.
Comment: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I felt so relieved it made me cry.
Comment: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised...
Comment: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the one that's surprised here.\NAre you okay? Should I walk you home first?
Comment: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I'm totally fine!\NThis type of thing tends to happen to girls.
Comment: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. Go on and get moving, Hikky.
Comment: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right... See you tomorrow. Get home safe.
Comment: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm practically home already.
Comment: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.67,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I'm glad my tears have stopped.
Comment: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:22.39,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,If I were crying, he wouldn't have left.
Comment: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.26,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,So I'm glad my tears stopped.
Comment: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:30.39,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I can't be a girl that people feel sorry for.
Comment: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:34.77,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,Because then, he'd just come and save me again.
Comment: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.32,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell him not to go.
Comment: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.20,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I couldn't ask him why he's helping her.
Comment: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.16,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I would hate to tell him to stop being so kind.
Comment: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:51.92,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I understand exactly what she's thinking\Nand what she's feeling.
Comment: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:58.67,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,But I could never give up, let go,\Nand refuse the way that she did.
Comment: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:04.97,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,It should all be so very easy, but... I can't do any of it.
Comment: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:09.06,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I considered it all her fault and just did nothing.
Comment: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:12.64,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who pushed things on everyone else.
Comment: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.69,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,That's why this is the way it should be, but...
Comment: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:22.78,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,Now and forever... my tears won't stop.
Comment: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:28.74,InsideYui,,0,0,0,,I wish my tears hadn't stopped then.
Comment: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,By Chance, Yui Yuigahama\NThinks of the Future.
Comment: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:38.19,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Looking back over and over again.
Comment: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:40.98,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Separated by distance, time passes...
Comment: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.15,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Going so far away that you can't return.
Comment: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:48.87,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,And at long last looking back to see what was right.
Comment: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:53.70,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Knowing you were wrong the whole time,\Nbut always saying this was the only answer.
Comment: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:55.75,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,As if to persuade yourself.
Comment: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.83,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Looking back over and over again.
Comment: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:04.17,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,But no longer stopping yourself\Nfrom taking a step forward.
